  continueButtonText: {fileID: 2076730166}
  slides:
  - 'Welcome!

    Click the Continue button to go to the next instruction'
  - You will assemble a drone from its parts.
  - There are 5 parts you need to connect, the 4 propellers and the battery.
  - When you pick the part, its ghost version will highlight showing you where to
    place it.
  - When close enough, release the part and it will snap into place.
  - 'Attach all the 5 parts to complete the drone.

    Good luck!

'
